POM - Test Desgin Frame work 

Cucumber - Testing Frame work - Which will helps us to reduce the lines of code and makes the testing easier

It uses Common Language - English

BDD - Behaviour data driven F/W 


CUCUMBER DEPENDENCY IN OUR POM.XML

<!-- https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/io.cucumber/cucumber-junit -->
<dependency>
    <groupId>io.cucumber</groupId>
    <artifactId>cucumber-junit</artifactId>
    <version>6.11.0</version>
    <scope>test</scope>
</dependency>

<!-- https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/io.cucumber/cucumber-java -->
<dependency>
    <groupId>io.cucumber</groupId>
    <artifactId>cucumber-java</artifactId>
    <version>6.11.0</version>
</dependency>




Feature File - English words [U r feeding how it should behave in english words] Using TAGS - @GIVEN , @WHEN , @THEN,  @AND

Step Definition - It will convert ur English words into a methods 

Test Runner - It will use Cucumber options which will glue ur Feature file and Step definition 


-- install cucumber plug in 